{"tid":1554799,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藍絲成日話冇中國香港就含撚","createTime":"2019-09-09T06:19:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T08:16:41.000Z","uid":204382,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"3a35d7f059b61538c28cf1aa270797c495697079","tid":1554799,"uid":204382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:19:17.000Z","msg":"佢哋成日話唔知1997、沙士、定金融海嘯冇中國救市香港就完,有冇熟時事或者經濟嘅ching可以解畫"},{"pid":"7fd07c311e8036b3973aa1093bd34684f8149025","tid":1554799,"uid":288559,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:21:24.000Z","msg":"咁咪試吓囉 睇下到時邊個含撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6e134e2445a641055d3b41698ea1413e753f61","tid":1554799,"uid":317299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:25:52.000Z","msg":"【913 八月十五】 金鐘悼義士<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1554687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1554687</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XySvw4Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXySvw4Z.jpg&h=8251e762&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hqGL5pZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhqGL5pZ.jpg&h=af6e3036&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2d51e9e33078d413874f6ce1ff311e67cee8986","tid":1554799,"uid":191762,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:27:20.000Z","msg":"三次都唔關中國事<br />\n九七係煲呔冇倚賴中國幫助之下擊退索羅斯<br />\n沙士係支那人帶落嚟香港<br />\n金融海嘯根本係全球經濟衰退中國自己都唔掂<br />\n<br />\n你可以同佢講鳩鐵香港段由香港起晒但係收益得兩成支那佔八成<br />\n港珠澳垃圾橋香港比最多嗰份（總成本一半）"},{"pid":"cc6aa2fbba7def62d592424358c9bb6b4a8b031e","tid":1554799,"uid":14941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:29:37.000Z","msg":"自由行又當初既益香港<br />\n變左毒癮禍害香港"},{"pid":"1c495dd9bbc870c295d3912285f3eb829fe91ff3","tid":1554799,"uid":166085,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTi